<div>
<p><span class="h-span">SCP-4790：</span>不要踏入静谧的良夜。<br />
<span class="h-span">作者：</span><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1735419); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735419&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606781488" alt="Lt Flops" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735419)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1735419); return false;">Lt Flops</a></span></p>
<p>本文设定于<strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/ad-astra-per-aspera-hub" target="_blank">循此苦旅，直抵群星</a></strong>。</p>
<hr />
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><span style="font-size:110%;"><span class="h-span">特别感谢——小动物和beta读者们：</span></span></p>
